		<title>Mayo Clinic researchers find “sugar coating” cells can protect those typically destroyed in type 1 diabetes</title>
		<link>https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/discussion/mayo-clinic-researchers-find-sugar-coating-cells-can-protect-those-typically-destroyed-in-type-1-diabetes/
		
