		<title>Mayo Clinic AI tool finds early signs of blood mutations linked to cancer&nbsp;and heart disease</title>
		<link>https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/discussion/mayo-clinic-ai-tool-finds-early-signs-of-blood-mutations-linked-to-cancer-and-heart-disease/
		
		<dc:creator><!--[CDATA[Susan Murphy]]--></dc:creator>
